{"tid":2172831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警犬患皮膚病　曬太陽治療期間暴斃","createTime":"2020-08-25T01:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T02:43:57.000Z","uid":333488,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"fd36dc51accc2e77cfab322e0111d031e4ac46b0","tid":2172831,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:27:42.000Z","msg":"警犬隊發生警犬死亡悲劇，消息稱，一隻5歲雄性德國牧羊警犬，經獸醫為診斷確診患有皮膚病，需要靠服藥及曬太陽控制病情，昨日(23日)放假時在觀塘行動基地曬太陽期間突然暴斃。據了解，該隻警犬屬緝毒及追蹤犬，事發時其領犬員亦放假。<br />\n<br />\n警犬隊較多以德國牧羊犬為主，該種狗隻性格忠心、勇敢、兼外形威武；適合與警方在巡邏進行日常工作。根據保安局於今年特別財委會回覆的文件顯示，警犬隊人手編制為168人，而截至今年2月於警隊服役的警犬數目為130隻，包括95隻巡邏犬及35隻嗅索犬，該批警犬的平均服役年期為7年。<br />\n<br />\n局方指，所有不適或受傷的警犬均會由註冊獸醫治理。由2016年至今年4月，警隊沒有警犬於服役時無故死亡；同期有9隻警犬因腫瘤、腎病和臗關節問題 等疾病死亡，全部個案均獲註冊獸醫跟進及確認。<br />\n<br />\nRIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635ab6ae023cbd483eddac6356d4e91965b62b71","tid":2172831,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:30:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654010dce0a00ec621b64051f09b9fcf7ee0fd38","tid":2172831,"uid":16676,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jCqsH6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4jCqsH6.jpg&h=90afee42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eH9sF27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeH9sF27.jpg&h=4865eaea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WNsNF28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWNsNF28.jpg&h=42b2fe08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因工殉職<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d2ac2bb6886c7491ee5d29f4e5c456fb0912b9","tid"